 522:               <!-- ====== 循环控制 ====== -->
 523:               <div class="settings-pane active" id="pane-loop">
 524:                 <div class="pane-head">
 525:                   <h2><span class="pane-ico"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-refresh"></use></svg></span> 循环控制</h2>
 526:                   <p>定义 AutoPlan 自动循环的工作区、节奏与验收方式。改动后点击底部「保存配置」生效。</p>
 527:                 </div>
 528: 
 529:                 <div class="set-card">
 530:                   <div class="set-card-head">
 531:                     <h3>工作区与节奏</h3>
 532:                     <div class="set-card-hint">循环在此目录下扫描 issues / plans，并执行任务与验收命令</div>
 533:                   </div>
 534:                   <div class="set-card-body">
 535:                     <div class="field">
 536:                       <span class="field-label">工作区路径 <span class="req">*</span></span>
 537:                       <input class="field-input mono" value="D:\project\GitHub\wenz_flutter\wenz_richtext" placeholder="D:\project\GitHub\my-app" />
 538:                       <span class="field-hint">循环在此目录下扫描 issues / plans，并执行任务与验收命令</span>
 539:                     </div>
 540:                     <div class="field">
 541:                       <span class="field-label">间隔秒数</span>
 542:                       <div class="input-affix">
 543:                         <input class="field-input" type="number" min="1" value="5" style="max-width:160px" />
 544:                         <span class="affix">秒</span>
 545:                       </div>
 546:                       <span class="field-hint">每轮之间的等待时间，最小 1 秒</span>
 547:                     </div>
 548:                     <div class="field">
 549:                       <span class="field-label">验收命令 <span class="tag">可选</span></span>
 550:                       <input class="field-input mono" value="flutter analyze" placeholder="留空则跳过外部验收命令" />
 551:                       <span class="field-hint">任务执行后运行；失败会触发重试，留空则不校验</span>
 552:                     </div>
 553:                   </div>
 554:                 </div>
 555: 
 556:                 <div class="settings-footer">
 557:                   <span class="dirty-note"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-alert"></use></svg>有未保存的更改</span>
 558:                   <div class="spacer">
 559:                     <button class="btn btn-sm" type="button">放弃更改</button>
 560:                     <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" type="button"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-save"></use></svg>保存配置</button>
 561:                   </div>
 562:                 </div>
 563:               </div>
 564: 
 565:               <!-- ====== CLI 后端 ====== -->
 566:               <div class="settings-pane" id="pane-cli">
 567:                 <div class="pane-head">
 568:                   <h2><span class="pane-ico"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-terminal"></use></svg></span> CLI 后端</h2>
 569:                   <p>选择执行任务的命令行后端。默认 Codex；历史项目未配置时按 Codex 兼容处理。</p>
 570:                 </div>
 571: 
 572:                 <div class="set-card">
 573:                   <div class="set-card-head">
 574:                     <h3>后端选择</h3>
 575:                     <div class="set-card-hint">切换后端会改变任务执行的命令行链路与可用能力</div>
 576:                   </div>
 577:                   <div class="set-card-body">
 578:                     <div class="field">
 579:                       <span class="field-label">后端</span>
 580:                       <div class="segmented" id="cliSegmented">
 581:                         <button class="seg-opt active" type="button" data-cli="codex">
 582:                           <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-code"></use></svg>
 583:                           Codex CLI <span class="seg-note">交互式</span>
 584:                         </button>
 585:                         <button class="seg-opt" type="button" data-cli="claude">
 586:                           <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-terminal"></use></svg>
 587:                           Claude CLI <span class="seg-note">-p 非交互</span>
 588:                         </button>
 589:                       </div>
 590:                       <span class="field-hint">Codex 支持会话复用与思考深度；Claude 仅覆盖非交互 <code>claude -p</code> 调用</span>
 591:                     </div>
 592: 
 593:                     <div class="field" id="effortField">
 594:                       <span class="field-label">
 595:                         <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" style="width:14px;height:14px;color:var(--text-3)"><use href="#icon-brain"></use></svg>
 596:                         Codex 思考深度
 597:                       </span>
 598:                       <div class="effort-grid">
 599:                         <button class="effort-opt" type="button" data-effort="low">
 600:                           <span class="eff-check"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-check"></use></svg></span>
 601:                           <span class="eff-name"><span class="eff-dot"></span>Low</span>
 602:                           <span class="eff-desc">速度优先，适合简单任务与高频循环</span>
 603:                         </button>
 604:                         <button class="effort-opt" type="button" data-effort="medium">
 605:                           <span class="eff-check"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-check"></use></svg></span>
 606:                           <span class="eff-name"><span class="eff-dot"></span>Medium</span>
 607:                           <span class="eff-desc">均衡选择，适合多数常规任务</span>
 608:                         </button>
 609:                         <button class="effort-opt" type="button" data-effort="high">
 610:                           <span class="eff-check"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-check"></use></svg></span>
 611:                           <span class="eff-name"><span class="eff-dot"></span>High</span>
 612:                           <span class="eff-desc">深度推理，适合复杂或跨文件任务</span>
 613:                         </button>
 614:                         <button class="effort-opt active" type="button" data-effort="xhigh">
 615:                           <span class="eff-check"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-check"></use></svg></span>
 616:                           <span class="eff-name"><span class="eff-dot"></span>XHigh</span>
 617:                           <span class="eff-desc">最高深度，适合架构级重构与难题攻坚</span>
 618:                         </button>
 619:                       </div>
 620:                       <span class="field-hint">仅 Codex CLI 生效，保存后下一轮执行参数使用该深度</span>
 621:                     </div>
 622: 
 623:                     <div class="provider-note" id="providerNote" style="display:none;">
 624:                       <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-info"></use></svg>
 625:                       <span>需本机已安装 <code>claude</code> CLI 并完成认证。Claude 不使用 Codex 会话复用与思考深度。</span>
 626:                     </div>
 627: 
 628:                     <div class="field">
 629:                       <span class="field-label">CLI 命令路径 <span class="tag">可选</span></span>
 630:                       <input class="field-input mono" value="" placeholder="留空用默认 codex" id="cliCmdInput" />
 631:                       <span class="field-hint">后端在 PATH 中时留空即可；否则填写可执行文件的完整路径</span>
 632:                     </div>
 633:                   </div>
 634:                 </div>
 635: 
 636:                 <div class="settings-footer">
 637:                   <span class="dirty-note"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-alert"></use></svg>有未保存的更改</span>
 638:                   <div class="spacer">
 639:                     <button class="btn btn-sm" type="button">放弃更改</button>
 640:                     <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" type="button"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-save"></use></svg>保存配置</button>
 641:                   </div>
 642:                 </div>
 643:               </div>
