 645:               <!-- ====== scope 文件打开方式 ====== -->
 646:               <div class="settings-pane" id="pane-scope">
 647:                 <div class="pane-head">
 648:                   <h2><span class="pane-ico"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-folder"></use></svg></span> scope 文件打开方式</h2>
 649:                   <p>Plan 全文中 scope 文件链接以该方式打开，路径限制在当前工作区内。</p>
 650:                 </div>
 651: 
 652:                 <div class="set-card">
 653:                   <div class="set-card-head">
 654:                     <h3>打开方式</h3>
 655:                     <div class="set-card-hint">系统默认 / 文件夹定位 / VSCode / 第三方编辑器命令</div>
 656:                   </div>
 657:                   <div class="set-card-body">
 658:                     <div class="field">
 659:                       <span class="field-label">打开方式</span>
 660:                       <div class="segmented" id="scopeSegmented">
 661:                         <button class="seg-opt" type="button" data-scope="system">
 662:                           <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-folder"></use></svg>系统默认
 663:                         </button>
 664:                         <button class="seg-opt" type="button" data-scope="folder">
 665:                           <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-folder"></use></svg>文件夹定位
 666:                         </button>
 667:                         <button class="seg-opt active" type="button" data-scope="vscode">
 668:                           <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-code"></use></svg>VSCode
 669:                         </button>
 670:                         <button class="seg-opt" type="button" data-scope="command">
 671:                           <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-terminal"></use></svg>第三方命令
 672:                         </button>
 673:                       </div>
 674:                       <span class="field-hint">第三方命令支持 <code>{file}</code> 占位</span>
 675:                     </div>
 676: 
 677:                     <div class="field" id="editorCmdField">
 678:                       <span class="field-label">编辑器命令 <span class="tag">可选</span></span>
 679:                       <input class="field-input mono" value="code" placeholder="code" id="editorCmdInput" />
 680:                       <span class="field-hint">选择 VSCode 时留空等价于 <code>code</code>；第三方命令例如 <code>cursor {file}</code></span>
 681:                     </div>
 682: 
 683:                     <div class="inline-banner info">
 684:                       <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-info"></use></svg>
 685:                       <span>打开前会校验目标路径位于当前工作区内；不存在、目录、越界路径或命令失败都会给出可读提示，不会静默失败。建议准确填写相对工作区的 scope，无法判断写 <b>unknown</b>、完整验收写 <b>validation</b>，避免错误并发。</span>
 686:                     </div>
 687:                   </div>
 688:                 </div>
 689: 
 690:                 <div class="settings-footer">
 691:                   <div class="spacer">
 692:                     <button class="btn btn-sm" type="button">放弃更改</button>
 693:                     <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" type="button"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-save"></use></svg>保存配置</button>
 694:                   </div>
 695:                 </div>
 696:               </div>
 697: 
 698:               <!-- ====== MCP 外部接入 ====== -->
 699:               <div class="settings-pane" id="pane-mcp">
 700:                 <div class="pane-head">
 701:                   <h2>
 702:                     <span class="pane-ico"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><use href="#icon-plug"></use></svg></span> MCP 外部接入
 703:                     <span class="mcp-status" style="margin-left:6px"><span class="led running" style="width:7px;height:7px;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--success-bg)"></span>运行中</span>
 704:                   </h2>
 705:                   <p>本机客户端可通过 MCP 工具创建项目、提交需求和反馈。以下为只读信息，不覆盖项目级 loop 配置。</p>
 706:                 </div>
 707: 
 708:                 <div class="set-card">
 709:                   <div class="set-card-head">
 710:                     <h3>服务信息</h3>
